On Wikipedia, "'''Naming conventions (sports)'''" could refer to one of a couple of article naming guidelines:

*[[Wikipedia:Naming conventions (sportspeople)]], guideline for naming articles about people who are known for participating in sports
*[[Wikipedia:Naming conventions (sports teams)]], guideline for naming articles about sports teams

